Enum Parent Class for emulating Enum's of other strong typed languages like C++, C# and Java

Usage: 

class MyEnum < Enum
  enum_attr :val1, 1
  enum_attr :val2, 2
end

e = MyEnum.new MyEnum::VAL2 # => #<MyEnum:0x007f968b2bef20 @attrs=2>
e.val2?	# => true
e.val1?	# => false
e.to_i	# => 2
e.val1 = true # => true
e.val1?	# => true

m = MyClass.new {myvar => "my var value", myenum => MyEnum::VAL1 }

